Enzyme-b'Angiotensin-transforming enzyme2 (ACE2) waa nooc ka mid ah enzyme-yada ku shaqeeya dhinaca dibadda ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka (celluulada).
ACE2 waxay aad ugu faa'iideysataa daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha iyo xididdada dhiigga, maadaama ay xakameyso shaqada angiotensin-II ee la xiriirta iyada oo la yareeyo heerarka Angiotensin-II iyo kordhinta heerarka Ang (1-7) sidoo kale waxay u shaqeysaa sidii albaabada u galaan unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa nooc ka mid ah xidhiidhka ku jira metalloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo kuwa kale.
Protein-ka ACE2 wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa borotiinka qanjirka ee nooca I ee hal-marinta, kaas oo ku dhaca dusha sare ee unugyada iyo unugyada kale ee unugyada iyada oo loo marayo domainka enzymically-activated.
Qaab-dhismeedka ka baxsan unugyada ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa unugyada unugyada unugyada iyada oo loo marayo enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, oo ka soo baxa borotiinka dhalaalaya ee dhiigga ku wareega, ugu dambeyntii waxaa loo sii daayaa cirbadaha.
ACE2 wuxuu ku jiraa qaybaha badan ee jirka - ACE2 wuxuu inta badan ku xirnaa unugyada unugyada unugyada nooca II ee unugyada unugyada, unugyada unugyada qanjirka 'antrocyte' ee mindhicirka, unugyada dhiigga iyo xididdada dhiigga iyo unugyada dhiigga ee unugyada jilicsan ee qaybaha badan ee jirka.
Soo bandhigida ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga heli karaa maskaxda dibedda ee maskaxda, qaybta maskaxda ee striatum, hoormoonnada jidhka loo baahan yahay, qaybta maskaxda ee hypothalamus iyo cerebrum, taas oo xakameynaysa nidaamka neerfaha iyo hoormoonnada.
Waxqabadka ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inuu ACE u adeego sidii xakameyn.
ACE waxay u dhejisaa angiotensin I hormoonka dhiigga oo ku dhajinaya angiotensin II.
ACE2 waxay ka soo saartaa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ka soo jeeda carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine, oo lagu dareero biyo-xakameyn ku saabsan angiotensin vasodilator (1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale la dagaallami kartaa qaar ka mid ah waxyaabaha kale ee loo yaqaan 'PAP' oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9]-brediquinine, epylene, neurotensin, dinophen A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareegga dhexdhexaadka ah ee xamuulka amino acid neutral SLC6A19 waxaana la xiriira cudurka Hartnup.
Protein-ka dhex-dhexaadka ah ee ACE2, ayaa ah mid ka mid ah meelaha loo aqbalo inay noqoto albaab-gacmeed muhiim u ah unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-ka, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63, SARS-CoV (virus-ka sababa SARS) iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka sababa COVID-19).
Si gaar ah, isku darka soo socda ee borotiinka SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee S1 ee ku jira domainka enzyme ee ACE2 ee dusha unugyada waxay keeni kartaa in fayraska iyo enzyme-ka ay galaan oo ay u wareegaan labada fayras iyo enzyme-ka gudaha unugyada gudaha ee ku yaal qolalka xakamaynta.
