Cudurka neefsashada ee halista daran ee Coronavirus-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2) waa cudurka neefsashada ee halista daran ee cusub ee ugu horreyn ka soo baxa saddex qof oo qaba cudurka sanbabada ee la xiriira bulshooyinka qaba cudurka neefsashada ee Wuhan.
